  "detailed_description": "You wake up in a place that is at once familiar and foreign to you. <br>With your abilities and memories damaged all you know is one thing:<br><br>You are the last Tetron, and the creatures here have cursed you, slaughtered your brethren, and are out to finish your race. <br><br>Now Is the Time For Vengeance.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect battle tomes to upgrade various aspects of your characters attack, defense, speed, or essence. </strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/4f2dbecd77952376974edb63ee6bb0bf.gif?t=1597418031\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/4f2dbecd77952376974edb63ee6bb0bf.poster.avif?t=1597418031\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Carefully manage your mana: should you save it for a devastating attack, or an upgrade?</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/d4a8005a25334d3cb15d093f0a1c4023.poster.avif?t=1597418031\" width=278 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/d4a8005a25334d3cb15d093f0a1c4023.webm?t=1597418031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/d4a8005a25334d3cb15d093f0a1c4023.mp4?t=1597418031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight the dangerous horde at night, or fall asleep near the warmth of the campfire. </strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/a3206e0d0ea8575040096641c836e2ac.poster.avif?t=1597418031\" width=278 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/a3206e0d0ea8575040096641c836e2ac.webm?t=1597418031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/a3206e0d0ea8575040096641c836e2ac.mp4?t=1597418031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/321e06d407846531ec62c5d178cb9eef.poster.avif?t=1597418031\" width=278 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/321e06d407846531ec62c5d178cb9eef.webm?t=1597418031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/321e06d407846531ec62c5d178cb9eef.mp4?t=1597418031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Traverse 3 areas each with various enemies, minibosses, bosses, and encounters.</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/445f73f018beb3130c2a756a394f77e6.poster.avif?t=1597418031\" width=278 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/445f73f018beb3130c2a756a394f77e6.webm?t=1597418031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/445f73f018beb3130c2a756a394f77e6.mp4?t=1597418031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348960/extras/5da4e8ab54675ab51b94f629c442629b.poster.avif?t=1597418031\" width=278 height=156 ><s